title: Hard Drives and Other Icons
description:
Custom icons I made based on standard OS X Icons

iTunes Drive- Internal Disc with itunes music note
iTunes Ext Drive- Custom ext. drive with itunes music note
iTunes lin icon- Custom iTunes App icon with inverted network icon
Lacie Drive- External Disk with Lacie logo and text
Media Drive- Hard drive with clapboard and Quicktime logo in middle
Media Drive 2- Same as 1 with clap & in bottom corner
Media Drive 3- Hard Drive with clapboard with red glow and Quicktime in bottom corner
Scratch Drive- Hard Drive with remix of Final Cut Pro app and file icon in corner
Time Machine Disk- 2 words- Flux Capacitor
XDisk- Hard Drive with big Leopard style X
XDisk 2- Slightly different style X
